umm, im not really sure if he used a script, my friend has 2b d chains on the juicyspace server, but the important thing to remember is that these can not be used in the real runescape, getting stuff like that is just for fun when you’re bored[br][size=1]Posted at: July 19, 2006, 09:19:16 AM[/size][hr]but if thats what you meant, you put in the name of the server you want to connect to, then play as if its runescape, the way you get stuff like that is through drops…for example my friend got p hats on the juicyscape server because whoever made that server put a high rate of christmas cracker as drops, same with d chains and so on
